{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"fengd's zone","author":"fengd"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"853c5f28-c40f-5d92-b678-d7d0b22fda6c","html":"<p>在安装 Plex Server 之前，先把系统升级到最新版。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> upgrade</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后添加 Plex Server 的官方代码库。在这之前还需要安装 apt-transport-https 包，来支持 apt 包管理软件从 https 读取包。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> apt-transport-https</code></pre></div>\n<p>添加安装源</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> https://downloads.plex.tv/plex-keys/PlexSign.key <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> deb https://downloads.plex.tv/repo/deb public main <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/plexmediaserver.list</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> plexmediaserver</code></pre></div>\n<p>默认情况下， plex media server 是以 plex 这个用户运行的，为了避免由于匿名用户造成的权限问题，把它改成以 pi 的用户身份运行。</p>\n<p>找到 /etc/default/plexmediaserver, 把 plex 改成 pi</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">PLEX_MEDIA_SERVER_USER</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>pi</code></pre></div>\n<p>重启生效</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl restart plexmediaserver</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"设置固定-ip-地址\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A-ip-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设置固定 IP 地址</h2>\n<p>作为一个资源库，当然是需要有一个固定 IP 会比较好，免得重启之后引起冲突</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">hostname</span> -I\n\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /boot/cmdline.txt\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">ip</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>YOUR IP</code></pre></div>\n<p>把 IP 设置为你的 IP， 然后重启树莓派</p>\n<h2 id=\"访问-web-站点\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE-web-%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>访问 Web 站点</h2>\n<p>我的 IP 地址是 192.168.3.52, 所以访问的地址是: <a href=\"http://192.168.3.52:32400/web/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://192.168.3.52:32400/web/index.html</a>,  我已经添加了不少资源</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/fc6fd/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 77.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"web admin\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/1c72d/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/a80bd/1.jpg 148w,\n/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/1c91a/1.jpg 295w,\n/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/1c72d/1.jpg 590w,\n/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/a8a14/1.jpg 885w,\n/static/45f960471fe7862999177bbdb8cca4e4/fc6fd/1.jpg 902w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>鼠标放到 播放列表 上，会出现添加按钮， 可以把想要添加进来的电影都添加进来</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/272bf/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 72.97297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"add library\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/1c72d/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/a80bd/2.jpg 148w,\n/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/1c91a/2.jpg 295w,\n/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/1c72d/2.jpg 590w,\n/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/a8a14/2.jpg 885w,\n/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/fbd2c/2.jpg 1180w,\n/static/57c93b77bf88780a154e77c0889cce0a/272bf/2.jpg 1466w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2 id=\"iphoneipadapple-tv-上使用\"><a href=\"#iphoneipadapple-tv-%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>iPhone/iPad/Apple TV 上使用</h2>\n<p>在 iPhone， iPad 或者 Apple TV 上使用，需要购买 Infuse Pro 这个软件，我记得是50块钱，但是物超所值。 这是在我的 iPhone 上，只要你在家里，随时随地可以看。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/b2cd5/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 216.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"library\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/1c72d/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/a80bd/3.jpg 148w,\n/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/1c91a/3.jpg 295w,\n/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/1c72d/3.jpg 590w,\n/static/8bf1ad1a5be497dabb565981c12972f4/b2cd5/3.jpg 828w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/b2cd5/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 216.2162162162162%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"add\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/1c72d/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/a80bd/4.jpg 148w,\n/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/1c91a/4.jpg 295w,\n/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/1c72d/4.jpg 590w,\n/static/07caddf29b957aa53d8cff4690dcc635/b2cd5/4.jpg 828w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"Setup Raspberry AS Media Library For Your Apple TV","date":"January 31, 2020","spoiler":"把 Raspberry 设置为一个 Plex Server， 配置 Infuse Pro， 可以作为 Apple TV 的媒体库"},"fields":{"slug":"/set-raspberry-pi-as-a-plex-server/","langKey":"en"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/set-raspberry-pi-as-a-plex-server/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/java-collection/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"java-collection"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Java 集合"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring-framework-components-one-beans/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"spring-framework-components-one-beans"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring Framework 基础组建探秘之 Beans"}},"translations":[],"translatedLinks":[]}}